been so for 30, 40 years.

00:12:55.610 --> 00:12:58.730 align:middle line:84%
>> Why do producers still
put nitrites in meat?

00:12:58.730 --> 00:13:03.080 align:middle line:84%
>> The main reason is that they
are afraid that customers will

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:07.070 align:middle line:84%
not accept products which do
not have the red color that they

00:13:07.070 --> 00:13:13.000 align:middle line:84%
