for many, many years.

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:15.855 align:middle line:84%
>> Hanegal is one of the few
food industry companies to do

00:13:15.855 --> 00:13:16.655 align:middle line:90%
without nitrites.

00:13:16.655 --> 00:13:20.760 align:middle line:90%


00:13:20.760 --> 00:13:23.940 align:middle line:84%
And yet, experts have been
ringing alarm bells for years.

00:13:23.940 --> 00:13:27.130 align:middle line:84%
25 years ago, a European
Union health report already

00:13:27.130 --> 00:13:29.560 align:middle line:84%
