00:13:46.145 --> 00:13:46.945 align:middle line:90%
to the products.

00:13:46.945 --> 00:13:54.383 align:middle line:90%


00:13:54.383 --> 00:13:55.800 align:middle line:84%
So we went to ask
the commissioner

00:13:55.800 --> 00:13:58.590 align:middle line:84%
