00:13:58.590 --> 00:14:00.855 align:middle line:90%
in Lithuania, a few questions.

00:14:00.855 --> 00:14:04.820 align:middle line:90%


00:14:04.820 --> 00:14:07.350 align:middle line:84%
>> Why don't get
