00:14:16.950 --> 00:14:20.820 align:middle line:84%
to follow, to say, and to
present to us final results.

00:14:20.820 --> 00:14:29.460 align:middle line:84%
And those always takes
time and responsibility.

00:14:29.460 --> 00:14:31.860 align:middle line:84%
>> For over an hour, the
commissioner attempted to pull

00:14:31.860 --> 00:14:36.270 align:middle line:84%
the wool over our eyes in spite
of all the reports by experts,

00:14:36.270 --> 00:14:39.450 align:middle line:84%
which for 25 years have
warned the authorities about

00:14:39.450 --> 00:14:41.820 align:middle line:90%
the dangers of nitrites.

00:14:41.820 --> 00:14:44.090 align:middle line:84%
>> All these studies, you
don't think they're enough?

00:14:44.090 --> 00:14:46.890 align:middle line:90%
>> All those studies are open.

00:14:46.890 --> 00:14:50.370 align:middle line:84%
And you see why thanks
