Sorry to say.

00:15:23.330 --> 00:15:24.600 align:middle line:90%
>> It's very [INAUDIBLE].

00:15:24.600 --> 00:15:30.180 align:middle line:84%
>> This study shows that all
standards are in safety line.

00:15:30.180 --> 00:15:35.040 align:middle line:84%
>> In this case, why Europe lost
against Denmark in the European

00:15:35.040 --> 00:15:37.410 align:middle line:84%
