00:15:48.610 --> 00:15:52.650 align:middle line:84%
>> So let's look at the
facts, Mr. Commissioner.

00:15:52.650 --> 00:15:55.770 align:middle line:84%
Denmark wanted to limit
the use of nitrites.

00:15:55.770 --> 00:15:58.300 align:middle line:84%
The European Commission
was against it.

00:15:58.300 --> 00:16:01.980 align:middle line:84%
And in 2003 in
court, the Danes won

00:16:01.980 --> 00:16:05.710 align:middle line:84%
in the name of the
