00:16:11.520 --> 00:16:13.980 align:middle line:90%
that public health is priority.

00:16:13.980 --> 00:16:17.840 align:middle line:84%
It means that DG Sante
and the commissioner

00:16:17.840 --> 00:16:21.990 align:middle line:84%
responsible for public health
is in better conditions.

00:16:21.990 --> 00:16:24.390 align:middle line:84%
>> And yet, since
this court ruling,

00:16:24.390 --> 00:16:28.440 align:middle line:84%
EU regulations are
just as lax as ever.

00:16:28.440 --> 00:16:32.280 align:middle line:84%
>> From my point of view,
we must be more energetic,

00:16:32.280 --> 00:16:34.995 align:middle line:84%
asking industry to change the
technology that formulates

00:16:34.995 --> 00:16:41.980 align:middle line:84%
food, to follow figures to
