00:16:41.980 --> 00:16:46.050 align:middle line:84%
priorities, not
profit, absolutely.

00:16:46.050 --> 00:16:48.870 align:middle line:90%
But, of course, it takes time.

00:16:48.870 --> 00:16:52.380 align:middle line:90%


00:16:52.380 --> 00:16:54.810 align:middle line:90%
>> Time, perfect.

00:16:54.810 --> 00:16:56.910 align:middle line:84%
That's just what the
food industry wants

00:16:56.910 --> 00:16:59.235 align:middle line:84%
and what it has built its
strategy on for years.

00:16:59.235 --> 00:17:08.339 align:middle line:90%


00:17:08.339 --> 00:17:10.109 align:middle line:84%
Because when it
comes to nitrites,

00:17:10.109 --> 00:17:15.790 align:middle line:84%
industrialists have been waiting
out the clock for 40 years,

00:17:15.790 --> 00:17:19.050 align:middle line:84%
40 years of scientific
manipulation, blackmail,

00:17:19.050 --> 00:17:21.599 align:middle line:84%
and intense lobbying
so the meat business

00:17:21.599 --> 00:17:23.760 align:middle line:84%
can carry on bringing
home the bacon.

00:17:23.760 --> 00:17:26.280 align:middle line:90%


00:17:26.280 --> 00:17:28.770 align:middle line:84%
And it all began on the
other side of the Atlantic.

00:17:28.770 --> 00:17:39.550 align:middle line:90%


00:17:39.550 --> 00:17:44.190 align:middle line:84%
If you think we're
exaggerating, listen to this.

00:17:44.190 --> 00:17:47.100 align:middle line:84%
In the late 1970s,
nitrite was almost

00:17:47.100 --> 00:17:50.340 align:middle line:84%
banned in the United States
just after the publication

00:17:50.340 --> 00:17:55.150 align:middle line:84%
of a large-scale study
requested by the government.

00:17:55.150 --> 00:17:58.860 align:middle line:84%
>> A relationship between
cancer and nitrite was proved,

00:17:58.860 --> 00:18:00.070 align:middle line:90%
suggested.

00:18:00.070 --> 00:18:02.100 align:middle line:84%
>> No, proved, and
a fairly strong one.

00:18:02.100 --> 00:18:05.400 align:middle line:84%
There were 2,000 rats
involved in this study.

00:18:05.400 --> 00:18:11.280 align:middle line:84%
It's a very extensive study done
by a well-respected scientist.

00:18:11.280 --> 00:18:14.460 align:middle line:84%
>> The banning of nitrites
was announced in the press,

00:18:14.460 --> 00:18:17.505 align:middle line:84%
but the American Meat Institute
would bring out its big guns.

00:18:17.505 --> 00:18:20.730 align:middle line:90%


00:18:20.730 --> 00:18:22.740 align:middle line:84%
