00:19:03.340 --> 00:19:04.610 align:middle line:90%
and cause an apocalypse.

00:19:04.610 --> 00:19:07.930 align:middle line:90%


00:19:07.930 --> 00:19:10.630 align:middle line:84%
But it was a political event
that would close the debate.

00:19:10.630 --> 00:19:15.170 align:middle line:90%


00:19:15.170 --> 00:19:17.420 align:middle line:84%
In 1980, Ronald
Reagan was elected

00:19:17.420 --> 00:19:19.250 align:middle line:90%
president of the United States.

00:19:19.250 --> 00:19:23.690 align:middle line:84%
And guess who entered
into government?

00:19:23.690 --> 00:19:26.690 align:middle line:84%
Richard Lyng, the president
of the American Meat Institute

00:19:26.690 --> 00:19:29.000 align:middle line:90%
himself.

00:19:29.000 --> 00:19:31.730 align:middle line:84%
The idea of banning
nitrite was forever buried.

00:19:31.730 --> 00:19:33.566 align:middle line:90%
[MECHANICAL CREAKING]

00:19:33.566 --> 00:19:36.320 align:middle line:90%


00:19:36.320 --> 00:19:39.320 align:middle line:84%
The experiment-based study
on 2,000 rats ended up

00:19:39.320 --> 00:19:40.120 align:middle line:90%
in the trash can.

00:19:40.120 --> 00:19:43.360 align:middle line:90%


00:19:43.360 --> 00:19:45.010 align:middle line:84%
And after that,
the same fate would

00:19:45.010 --> 00:19:46.990 align:middle line:84%
await every
scientific publication

00:19:46.990 --> 00:19:49.376 align:middle line:90%
calling nitrites into question.

00:19:49.376 --> 00:19:51.268 align:middle line:90%
[BOINGING]

00:19:51.268 --> 00:19:55.060 align:middle line:90%


00:19:55.060 --> 00:19:57.310 align:middle line:84%
If you're wondering how
the interests of industry

00:19:57.310 --> 00:19:59.290 align:middle line:84%
can systematically
win against what's

00:19:59.290 --> 00:20:05.010 align:middle line:84%
at stake in public health, the
following will enlighten you.

00:20:05.010 --> 00:20:07.650 align:middle line:84%
15 years after the victory
of Reagan and the meat

00:20:07.650 --> 00:20:11.995 align:middle line:84%
industrialists, a new study
shook America to the core.

00:20:11.995 --> 00:20:13.620 align:middle line:84%
>> If it's not one
thing, it's another.

00:20:13.620 --> 00:20:17.220 align:middle line:84%
