scientist living

00:20:59.720 --> 00:21:02.900 align:middle line:84%
near Los Angeles in a
residential, suburban setting

00:21:02.900 --> 00:21:04.490 align:middle line:84%
straight out of
an American soap.

00:21:04.490 --> 00:21:09.020 align:middle line:90%


00:21:09.020 --> 00:21:12.440 align:middle line:84%
