talks, she agreed to see us.

00:21:12.440 --> 00:21:18.480 align:middle line:90%


00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:21.750 align:middle line:84%
But we had to insist right
up until the last minute.

00:21:21.750 --> 00:21:24.630 align:middle line:90%


00:21:24.630 --> 00:21:26.520 align:middle line:90%
The lady is very discreet.

