rare cancers in children.

00:21:59.350 --> 00:22:02.560 align:middle line:90%


00:22:02.560 --> 00:22:05.830 align:middle line:84%
>> How did you find
the relationship?

00:22:05.830 --> 00:22:08.610 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, just the way we always
did when we did case control

00:22:08.610 --> 00:22:09.410 align:middle line:90%
