leukemia ate more hot dogs.

00:22:23.820 --> 00:22:26.320 align:middle line:84%
>> What did you think when you
saw this strong relationship?

00:22:26.320 --> 00:22:28.112 align:middle line:84%
Because it was quite
a strong relationship.

00:22:28.112 --> 00:22:29.140 align:middle line:90%
>> It was with hot dogs.

00:22:29.140 --> 00:22:36.140 align:middle line:84%
I was a little bit
surprised and just reserved

00:22:36.140 --> 00:22:38.780 align:middle line:84%
judgment, which is
what epidemiologists

00:22:38.780 --> 00:22:42.810 align:middle line:84%
